{"title":"让 Agent 符合预期的十大实战经验","uid":"6ebc4ccffa76c9af624a449c5f55274e","slug":"让Agent符合预期的十大实战经验","date":"2026-07-16T02:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-07-16T02:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/让Agent符合预期的十大实战经验.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/让Agent符合预期的十大实战经验.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"“为什么调了提示词，Agent-效果还是差？”\"><a href=\"#“为什么调了提示词，Agent-效果还是差？”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"“为什么调了提示词，Agent 效果还是差？”\"></a>“为什么调了提示词，Agent 效果还是差？”</h2><p>阿里云”云小二 Aivis”团队在近一年的 Multi-Agent 实践中踩过大量坑，从真实踩坑中总结出十条行之有效的经验。</p>\n<p>在深入之前，先搞清楚一个前提：<strong>你的预期到底是什么？</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>“希望它更智能一点”、”它应该正确回答问题”——这些都是模糊预期，无法指导有效优化。</p></blockquote>\n<p>好的预期应该包含三个维度：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>维度</th>\n<th>模糊预期</th>\n<th>清晰预期</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>任务</strong></td>\n<td>“判断安全组是否放行”</td>\n<td>端口为 -1&#x2F;-1 且 IP 为 0.0.0.0 且策略为 Accept → 完全放行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>格式</strong></td>\n<td>“给个诊断报告”</td>\n<td>输出 JSON，含 instance_id、problem_category、conclusion 字段</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>风格</strong></td>\n<td>“回复要友好”</td>\n<td>诊断超 3 步未解决时，以歉意语气回复”非常抱歉，正在深入排查…”</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"十大经验速查\"><a href=\"#十大经验速查\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十大经验速查\"></a>十大经验速查</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>#</th>\n<th>经验</th>\n<th>一句话</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>上下文精准投喂</td>\n<td>给其所需，去其所扰</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>身份与历史清晰化</td>\n<td>不要 Mask 掉模型的真实执行历史</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>结构化表达逻辑</td>\n<td>复杂流程用 JSON&#x2F;伪代码，别只用自然语言</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>自定义工具协议</td>\n<td>领域化协议可能比通用协议更稳</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Few-Shot 合理使用</td>\n<td>单任务多用（注重多样性），灵活任务慎用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>保持上下文苗条</td>\n<td>超过 1 万 Token 遗忘率显著增加</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>记忆管理</td>\n<td>多次增强 + 上下文压缩 + 外部存储</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>Multi-Agent 平衡</td>\n<td>Workflow 控稳定，LLM 控灵活</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>自定义协议补充</td>\n<td>领域场景值得尝试，但要能维护</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>HITL 人在回路</td>\n<td>先搞清楚”人”是怎么做的</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"逐条拆解\"><a href=\"#逐条拆解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"逐条拆解\"></a>逐条拆解</h2><h3 id=\"1-上下文精准投喂\"><a href=\"#1-上下文精准投喂\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 上下文精准投喂\"></a>1. 上下文精准投喂</h3><p><strong>给其所需，去其所扰。</strong> 该给的信息没给全，不该给的信息给太多——这是 Agent 效果不佳最常见的两个原因。</p>\n<p>典型踩坑：财务工具返回十几个字段（可用金、冻结金额、信用金额……），一股脑塞给模型后，结论每次都不一样。正确做法是做一层<strong>信息筛选</strong>，只透传模型判断时真正需要的字段。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>模型困惑时不会”承认自己不懂”，而是自由发挥——这才是幻觉的真正来源。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"2-身份与历史执行清晰化\"><a href=\"#2-身份与历史执行清晰化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 身份与历史执行清晰化\"></a>2. 身份与历史执行清晰化</h3><p><strong>模型需要明确知道有几方身份、自己做过哪些事。</strong></p>\n<p>典型踩坑：把客服小二的对话直接当 History 喂给模型”续写”下一步动作，结果模型没调工具就直接编造了答案。根因是模型从 History 中”学”到了不调工具直接回复的模式，且”小二”的 Assistant 角色和模型的 Assistant 角色混淆。</p>\n<p>正确做法：用户 ↔ 模型的交互作为主线；小二对话标为”参考记忆”；模型自己执行过的 Action History <strong>完整保留</strong>。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>不要删除模型的真实执行历史，即使是那些”错误”的尝试。<strong>擦除失败会移除证据，没有证据模型就无法适应。</strong>（Manus：”Keep the Wrong Stuff In”）</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"3-结构化表达逻辑\"><a href=\"#3-结构化表达逻辑\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 结构化表达逻辑\"></a>3. 结构化表达逻辑</h3><p>大模型对 JSON、YAML、伪代码的理解能力远强于纯自然语言。”先调 A → 再调 B → 再调 C”这种流程，写成结构化形式遵循能力会好很多。</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-自定义工具协议\"><a href=\"#4-自定义工具协议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 自定义工具协议\"></a>4. 自定义工具协议</h3><p>云小二团队从 2023 年就开始 Agent 探索，自定义了一套工具协议。后来与 OpenAI Function Call 和 Anthropic MCP 做兼容测试——<strong>领域场景下自定义协议的准确性和稳定性反而优于通用协议</strong>。可能原因：模型为通用协议训练时逻辑固化，遇到你的领域需求不会完全遵循你的指令。</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-Few-Shot-合理使用\"><a href=\"#5-Few-Shot-合理使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. Few-Shot 合理使用\"></a>5. Few-Shot 合理使用</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>场景</th>\n<th>建议</th>\n<th>原因</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>单任务（抽取&#x2F;判断）</td>\n<td>✅ 多用，注重<strong>多样性</strong></td>\n<td>不同类型各给一条，效果比 1-2 条好得多</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>灵活开放任务（生成回复）</td>\n<td>❌ 慎用或不用</td>\n<td>模型容易”过拟合”示例，甚至把 Few-Shot 和工具返回搞混</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>灵活任务效果不佳时，与其硬塞 Few-Shot，不如开启模型的”深度思考”让它多想一步。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"6-保持上下文的”苗条”\"><a href=\"#6-保持上下文的”苗条”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. 保持上下文的”苗条”\"></a>6. 保持上下文的”苗条”</h3><p>大模型号称支持百万级 Token，但实测超过 1 万 Token 后遗忘率显著增加——System Prompt 里的核心要求都可能被”间歇性遗忘”。</p>\n<p>建议：通过 RAG 动态筛选、删减重复提示词、测试移除某条指令后模型反应是否敏感。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>一个高效的 Agent，一定是精雕细琢的结果，不是”堆料”堆出来的。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"7-记忆管理三层策略\"><a href=\"#7-记忆管理三层策略\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7. 记忆管理三层策略\"></a>7. 记忆管理三层策略</h3><p>随着对话越来越长，模型遗忘越来越明显。三层策略：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>多次增强</strong>：关键信息（实例 ID、IP 等）定期追加到对话中，或在工具入参出参中持续传入传出</li>\n<li><strong>上下文压缩</strong>（”内存”）：最近 3-5 轮之外的 History 用 summary 精简</li>\n<li><strong>外部存储</strong>（”外存”）：长期信息（咨询历史、用户画像）存入 Memory 池，按需查询注入</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"8-Multi-Agent-平衡\"><a href=\"#8-Multi-Agent-平衡\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8. Multi-Agent 平衡\"></a>8. Multi-Agent 平衡</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>角色</th>\n<th>职责</th>\n<th>实现方式</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>主 Agent</strong></td>\n<td>意图路由、调度决策</td>\n<td>LLM 自主决策 + 业务经验约束，<strong>偏灵活</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>子 Agent</strong></td>\n<td>复杂诊断、固定流程</td>\n<td>Workflow 编排 或 单任务 LLM，<strong>偏稳定</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>强流程模块收敛到子 Agent，需要灵活处理的部分交给主 Agent。既可控又灵活。</p>\n<h3 id=\"9-领域化协议优化\"><a href=\"#9-领域化协议优化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"9. 领域化协议优化\"></a>9. 领域化协议优化</h3><p>即使业界标准在统一，领域化的协议优化依然有价值。如果你发现模型在标准协议下对领域指令执行不够稳定，不妨自己定制一套——前提是你能维护好它。</p>\n<h3 id=\"10-HITL-人在回路\"><a href=\"#10-HITL-人在回路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10. HITL 人在回路\"></a>10. HITL 人在回路</h3><p>Agent 的本质是让大模型”模拟”<strong>人</strong>的行为。想做好 Agent，你必须先知道”人”是怎么做的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>人是如何识别这个问题的？</li>\n<li>什么情况应该查哪个工具？</li>\n<li>查到结果后如何回复？</li>\n</ul>\n<p>做 Agent 就像”明星模仿秀”——不深入研究这个明星的造型、动作、演唱技巧，就模仿不像。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>云小二团队做 Aivis 时，研发需要不停与客服、督导沟通，甚至去现场观察真实的接单过程，才能做出适合客服使用的数字员工。<strong>做 Agent 的人必须深入一线。</strong></p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>参考来源</strong>：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/u6F93L0sCfR-rjqBSJi3lQ\">如何让Agent更符合预期？基于上下文工程和多智能体构建云小二Aivis的十大实战经验</a></p></blockquote>\n","text":"阿里云\"云小二 Aivis\"团队基于真实业务踩坑，总结出十大 Agent 优化经验。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":15,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"AI","slug":"AI","count":19,"path":"api/tags/AI.json"},{"name":"Agent","slug":"Agent","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Agent.json"},{"name":"上下文工程","slug":"上下文工程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/上下文工程.json"},{"name":"Multi-Agent","slug":"Multi-Agent","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Multi-Agent.json"},{"name":"阿里云","slug":"阿里云","count":1,"path":"api/tags/阿里云.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%B0%83%E4%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E8%AF%8D%EF%BC%8CAgent-%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%9F%E2%80%9D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">“为什么调了提示词，Agent 效果还是差？”</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">十大经验速查</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%90%E6%9D%A1%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">逐条拆解</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E6%8A%95%E5%96%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 上下文精准投喂</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E5%8C%96\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 身份与历史执行清晰化</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 结构化表达逻辑</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4. 自定义工具协议</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-i